<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca95f91a-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2901"><num value="2901">§ 2901.</num><heading> Purpose</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purpose of this chapter is to facilitate the transfer of title to Reclamation project facilities to qualifying entities on the completion of repayment of capital costs.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca95f91b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/116/9/tVIII/s8001">Pub. L. 116–9, title VIII, § 8001</ref>, <date date="2019-03-12">Mar. 12, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/133/804">133 Stat. 804</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
